description:
This is a 18 minute workout called '15 MIN DAILY STRETCH (full body) - for tight muscles, mobility & flexibility' from the channel MadFit.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Stretching and Flexibility/Yoga.
It's suitable for Beginner fitness levels.
The workout has a The Zen Flow and The Reboot Workout vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: This is a quick, relaxing, full body stretch you can add into your daily routine! This 15 min stretch focuses on stretching tight muscles, and working on flexibility & mobility. Perfect to do first thing in the morning, before bed, or even after a workout. #fitness #yoga #homeworkout
